                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7275" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0185</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7743 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医同发展，检康共享：金域医学社会责任的实践创新之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Development of medicine and sharing of &quot;examination&quot; and &quot;health&quot;: a practical and innovative way of KingMed diagnastics social responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李红，段雨欣，何嘉煜，夏亚婷，吴晓崧，张路坤</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南昌大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广州金域医学检验集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金域医学集团；社会责任创新；战略性企业社会责任；社会责任生态系统</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">KingMed diagnastics; Social responsibility innovation; Strategic corporate social responsibility; Social responsibility ecosystem; 2022 top 100 cases</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在新冠疫情背景下，第三方医检行业异军突起，我国卫生与健康事业发展进入新时期。广州金域医学检验集团作为第三方医检现代化、国际化的领军者，始终以“健康哨兵，追求人类健康美好生活”为企业使命，积极进行数字化转型，进军大健康领域。在企业发展的同时，金域医学从设立集团培育发展中心、十年援藏资源普及、贫困区产业扶贫、振新老区汲取前进力量等各个方面进行社会责任实践创新，回报社会。金域医学立足创新发展理念实现为社会提供更优质的服务，顺应大健康产业供给侧改革趋势，升级数字化转型战略，融合“产学研医”各界力量共同打造以“医检服务全流程智能化、生命科技与新一代信息技术融合创新、生态平台共创共生共赢”为特点的“医检4.0”，实现企业与社会共享发展。本案例主要介绍了金域医学如何将履行社会责任与企业发展战略相结合，进行社会责任实践创新，打造社会责任生态系统，以实现企业高质量可持续发展的做法和经验。通过本案例的学习，旨在帮助学员学习和理解社会责任的内涵、履行方式及创新实践对企业的影响，为其他企业的社会责任实践创新提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of the COVID-19, the third-party medical examination industry has sprung up, and China&#39;s health and health undertakings have entered a new era. As a leader in the modernization and internationalization of third-party medical examination, Guangzhou KingMed diagnastics examination group has always taken &quot;health sentry, pursuit of human health and a better life&quot; as its corporate mission, actively carried out digital transformation and entered the field of great health. At the same time of enterprise development, KingMed diagnastics has carried out social responsibility practice and innovation in various aspects, such as the establishment of the group&#39;s cultivation and development center, the popularization of ten-year aid to Tibet resources, the industrial poverty alleviation in poor areas, and the drawing of forward forces from the revitalization of old areas, so as to repay the society. Based on the innovative development concept, KingMed medicine has realized to provide better services for the society, complied with the supply side reform trend of the big health industry, upgraded the digital transformation strategy, and combined the forces of &quot;industry, University, research and medicine&quot; from all walks of life to jointly create a &quot;medical examination 4.0&quot; characterized by &quot;intelligent whole process of medical examination services, integrated innovation of life technology and new generation information technology, and co creation of symbiosis and win-win ecological platform&quot;, so as to realize the shared development of enterprises and society. This case mainly introduces the practice and experience of KingMed medicine on how to combine the performance of social responsibility with enterprise development strategy, carry out social responsibility practice innovation, and create a social responsibility ecosystem to achieve high-quality sustainable development of enterprises. Through the study of this case, the purpose is to help students learn and understand the connotation of social responsibility, the way of performance and the impact of innovation practice on enterprises, and provide reference for other enterprises&#39; social responsibility practice innovation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《商业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任定义及金字塔模型；战性企业社会责任定义、特征及与非战略性企业社会责任区别；企业社会责任与企业战略的融合机制；企业社会责任战略类型、企业社会责任生态系统</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-04</td>
                            </tr>
